%p{style: "margin:0 0 6px;font-size:15px;color:#4b5563;line-height:1.6;"}
  Welcome #{@email}!
%p{style: "margin:0 0 16px;font-size:15px;color:#4b5563;line-height:1.6;"} You can confirm your account email through the link below:
%table{width: "100%", cellpadding: "0", cellspacing: "0", border: "0", style: "margin-top:8px;"}
  %tr
    %td{align: "center"}
      %a{href: confirmation_url(@resource, confirmation_token: @token), style: "display:inline-block;padding:11px 28px;background-color:#4a5e82;color:#ffffff;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;border-radius:6px;"}
        Confirm my account
